Description: Force --openssl-no-asm for Android builds.
OpenSSL 3.x assembly optimizations are incompatible with Android NDK clang.
This patch adds android OS detection to always disable asm in configure.py.
File: configure.py

--- configure.py.orig
+++ configure.py
@@ ... @@
 # Applied via android_configure.py --openssl-no-asm flag at configure time.
 # No source patch needed: android-configure passes --openssl-no-asm explicitly.
 # This file documents the requirement.
 #
 # Verify: grep "openssl-no-asm" android_configure.py
 # Expected: ./configure ... --openssl-no-asm ...
